title: EROS MODIS Normalized Difference Vegetation Index: 2001-Present
name: eros-modis-normalized-difference-vegetation-index71862
notes: eMODIS processes calibrated radiance data (level-1B) acquired by the MODIS sensors on the EOS Terra and Aqua satellites by combining MODIS Land Science Collection 5 Atmospherically Corrected Surface Reflectance production code and USGS EROS MODIS Direct Broadcast System (DBS) software to create surface reflectance and Normalized Difference Vegetation Index (NDVI) products.
